<span class="timeline">Week 2</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">3</div>
<h3>Strategy Development</h3>
<p>Create detailed growth strategy with specific initiatives, timelines, and targets.</p>
<span class="timeline">Week 3-4</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">4</div>
<h3>Quick Wins</h3>
<p>Implement immediate improvements for rapid results and momentum.</p>
<span class="timeline">Month 1-2</span>
</div>
<div class="process-step">
<div class="step-number">5</div>
<h3>Scale & Optimize</h3>
<p>Execute full strategy, measure results, and continuously optimize for growth.</p>
<span class="timeline">Month 3+</span>
</div>
